      "name": "Monte Carlo UQ — hemolysis index uncertainty bands",
      "description": "Monte Carlo propagation of inlet velocity and blood viscosity uncertainty through the CFD hemolysis model. 95th-percentile prediction interval spans ±31% of the mean hemolysis index, indicating substantial parametric sensitivity. A screening sensitivity exercise ranked inlet boundary conditions as the dominant uncertainty contributor, but no structured SensitivityAnalysis record was generated as part of this credibility package."
    }
