      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic pump geometry, which differs from the target VAD geometry in impeller blade angle and gap clearance. Operating conditions cover only 3 of 5 required flow-speed combinations. COU fidelity mapping document is incomplete. Achieved level 2 is below required level 5."
    },
    {
