      "rationale": "Solver convergence is monitored via residual drop to 1e-5 for flow variables, but hemolysis scalar transport residuals are not separately tracked. No floating-point sensitivity or tolerance study has been performed. This factor is flagged as an epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level 1 reflects absence of assessment."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
